title: Amy’s Husband Eats A Bug + Lunchbox Wants His Wife To Sell Breast Milk

description:
Amy explains the reason her husband ate a bug in front of their son. Lunchbox has a new business idea that involves selling his wife’s breast milk. Also, Bobby talks about the tattoo he will get with his partner Sharna if he wins Dancing With The Stars.
